            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Governance is the organizational layer — policies, roles, and approval workflows. Guardrails are the technical layer — the actual filters, classifiers, and moderation systems that enforce those policies at runtime, on every request and every response.</p></div></div>
